Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through!\NI said, let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to deliver\Nthe students' congratulatory speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd have the pleasure\Nof seeing you off the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought nothing could ever\Nsurprise me again, but these are chaotic times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The groom Sir Alexis Deux,\Nand bride Marrine Kreische.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Entering!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The union between these youths\Nsymbolizes the end of the longstanding war
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,between the Alliance and the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The unification of our family Crests
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will result in the creation of the Grancrest,\Nthe Emperor's Holy Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And after being ravaged by endless chaos,\NAtlatan will know peace at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way...\NChaos Convergence?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're in danger. Please step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Who are you?\N- What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!\NI must disperse the Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Lord of Diabolos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must help the archdukes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Lord has raised\Na dimensional barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Erupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why has the Demon Lord appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can nothing be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bow down before my Crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's Archduke Kreische's Crest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a massive, complex glow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will assist you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Emperor's Holy Seal, the Grancrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That should be enough to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the Grand Hall Tragedy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the magical city of Aram,\Non the Atlatan Continent,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}split in two by the Factory Federation\Nand the Fantasy Alliance,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the union of the two archdukes’ families\Nwas broken by this incident.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream for peace was shattered,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the flames of war rose once again\Nacross the entire continent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's about time\Nyou stopped sulking, Lady Siluca?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to serve some lewd count?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He'll only sign contracts with female students\Nfrom the magic university.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plus he picks them based on their looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And don't get me started\Non this heinous uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know he's a big shot Alliance noble,\Nbut really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've half a mind to void this contract\Nand go back to Aram!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But contracts between mage and master\Nare absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that town was destroyed\Nby the Chaos as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's on their negligent Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you're an oddball, aren't you Irvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Being the Kreische family's chamberlain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd leave your post\Nto serve a fledgling mage like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't stopped you, Lady Siluca,\NI might've saved my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I left my post with the Kreische family\Nto atone for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Siluca.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You on the carriage, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We know there's a mage\Nriding in that carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The one entering into a contract\Nwith Vilar, the Count of Artuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our Lord is a member of the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Count of Artuk is with the Alliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we can't allow mages\Nunder contract with him to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking a mage before her contract begins\Nis a violation of the treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the contract is set,\Nthen she's considered our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Siluca...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's come to this, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can have your way with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- So eager!\N- Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you no sense,\Nattacking an innocent on the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Crest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That youth appears to be a Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at that power level,\Nhe can't even call himself a Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a Lord from the Alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I belong to neither the Alliance\Nnor the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The opposition has both a mage and a Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say they can take on\Na hundred opponents, single-handedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but rumors!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was promised a Crest from our Lord\Nif we succeed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And once I have a Crest,\Neven I'll have a shot at becoming a Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crests are for protecting the people\Nfrom the Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Crests didn't fall into the hands\Nof ill-intentioned people like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there would be no meaningless wars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse,\NI'll show you no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets into trouble, help him out.\NI'd like to see what he’s capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's just one man!\NSurround him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one would accuse him\Nof having good sword skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, I wouldn't say\Nthat he doesn't have potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have in mind, Lady Siluca?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what you're thinking yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you to refrain, but just as a formality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I've already made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's no concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that.\NDon’t you have something to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you for saving me from such peril!"\NSomething like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of thanking you,\Nsince I wasn't in any danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was no need to rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your way of saying I butted in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:10:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Siluca Meletes, a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That man is Irvin, a demon seal holder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you receive your Crest from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Receive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is something I made\Nto exterminate demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You made a Crest from the Chaos Core?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what kind of world\Ndo you wish to create with that Crest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,World?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Systina, where I was born,\Nhas a high concentration of Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Demons run rampant there.\NAnd there are frequent natural disasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, scores of my people suffer under\Nthe tyranny of the Alliance's Viscount Rossini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I receive my title,\NI'm going to head home and become a Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to suppress the Chaos with my Crest,\Nrepulse the demons and prevent disasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those are fine intentions you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at your rank, you couldn't rule over\Na single town, let alone Systina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could always pledge fealty to Rossini,\Nand have him make you a Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wish to serve a man like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're giving up your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to raise my rank\Nby enhancing my own powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many years it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This world is rife with Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Order has been lost,\Nand the laws of nature have been disrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hence why we see impossible phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One of them being the emergence\Nof demons from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which cast a shadow...\NOver this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Converge!\NFrom Tartarus into Orthros!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Crest's potency is determined\Nby the amount of Chaos it contains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you defeat this and absorb its Chaos Core,\Nyou can attain the rank of Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, I'm going to haunt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have it any other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was sure my number was up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You better hurry,\Nor the Chaos Core will disperse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Crest has reached the rank of Knight!\NYou can enter into a contract with one mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do that with someone\Nother than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am already committed to a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you still want me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I never said that, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, Siluca Meletes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...hereby enter into contract\Nwith the Crest of Knight Theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and swear eternal allegiance to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one forcing yourself on me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just give yourself to fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, shall we set off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To war!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Mesto, just what were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking a mage before her contract goes\Ninto effect is a major violation of our treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're charged,\Nthey could strip you of your rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why should Lords like us be stifled\Nby the damn Mages' Association's rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, you need to consult\NViscount Shakes, the leader of Clovis–
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you need to do is follow my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Lord named Theo is demanding\Nthat you hand over your Crest and castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is this Lord from?\NHow many men are we up against?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Only three?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who does he think he's dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does he really think he can seize this castle\Nwith just three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that’s enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Siluca Meletes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Siluca?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That you were sure to master every subject,\Nand become a Rainbow Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disappoint you.\NI graduated with six colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the mage entering\Ninto a contract with the Count of Artuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'm now under contract\Nto Sir Theo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain?\NA mage who unilaterally voids a contract
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will be penalized accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I believe this is destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing, Sartorus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I order you in the name of my Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hurry and deal with these–\N- Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've violated the treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning you'll be stripped\Nof your rank and everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And your contract with me is now void.\NI have no reason to follow your orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this,\Nit's time to surrender your Crest,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and leave this land without further delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because you passed\Nthrough my domain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Crest or your life,\Nwhich will you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anything but my life...\NPlease spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\Nrelinquish your Crest to my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, Mesto Meadrich, offer my Crest\Nto you as your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold out your Crest, Sir Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, Theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, Theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Accept thy Crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Accept thy Crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and receive it as my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and receive it as my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now, please lay\Nyour own Crest against Mesto's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, he seems pitiful, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The people living under such\Na foolish Lord should be pitied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you hadn't seized it, a Lord like that\Nwould've lost his Crest eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, this means that along with his Crest,\Nyou've inherited that Lord's domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But whether the other Lords\Nin this area will recognize that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to go speak with Viscount Shakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is, if Sir Theo will agree\Nto enter a contract with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome the chance to have a mage\Nwith your experience and common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall set off\Nto negotiate immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because Sir Theo is going\Nto announce that he’s joining the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if he does,\Nhe’ll be surrounded by enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely what our Lord desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are you planning\Nto make me do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That I was going to help you realize\Nthe world you've envisioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I could end up dead\Nbefore I ever realize my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you'll have me by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CONTRACT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 2:\NAMBITION
